   "providers": {                                                                                                                                                                     
     "nyro": {                                                                                                                                                                        
       "modelOverrides": {                                                                                                                                                            
         "deepseek-v4-flash-2": {                                                                                                                                                     
           "compat": {                                                                                                                                                                
             "sendSessionIdHeader": true                                                                                                                                              
           }                                                                                                                                                                          
         }                                                                                                                                                                            
       }                                                                                                                                                                              
     }                                                                                                                                                                                
   }                                                                                                                                                                                  
 }

arguments.task:
Read ~/.pi/agent/models.json. If the file doesn't exist, create it. Then add the `sendSessionIdHeader` compat setting for the nyro provider.

The user's recommended override is either a provider-level minimal override:
```json
{
  "providers": {
    "nyro": {
      "compat": {
        "sendSessionIdHeader": true
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Or a single-model override if only deepseek-v4-flash-2 should change:
```json
{
  "providers": {
    "nyro": {
      "modelOverrides": {
        "deepseek-v4-flash-2": {
          "compat": {
            "sendSessionIdHeader": true
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Use the single-model override approach if the file has existing modelOverrides or per-model config. Use the provider-level approach otherwise. Merge with any existing content in the file — don't clobber other providers/models.

